I must tell my secret to the whole world<br />
Because I&#8217;m happy<br />
The whole world is now twice as important to me<br />
Because now I know what happiness is</p>
<p>But isn&#8217;t this world too busy?<br />
Who still has time for happiness?<br />
Yet I want to cheer because<br />
I must tell my secret to the whole world<br />
Because I&#8217;m happy</p>
<p>Shall I write cards to let everyone know?<br />
Shall I advertise in the paper?<br />
